                     <hi rend="largeCaps">ROBERT LLOYD</hi>
                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18371127-32-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18371127-32-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18371127-32-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp> for that he feloniously did utter, dispose of, and put off a certain forged receipt for 18<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., well knowing the same to be forged, with intent to defraud <persName id="t18371127-name-244" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18371127-name-244" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18371127-name-244" type="surname" value="PONTIFEX"></interp>
